{"tid":1281821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立即停止討論自己嘅夢境！！！","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T05:12:03.000Z","uid":179379,"like":368,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"99592c2ab8a923630aa7dd4a8de83cb97ff4551b","tid":1281821,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"我知大家因為白色恐怖好大壓力，我自己都係<br />\n但如你繼續將自己嘅夢境放上網，只會令你更危險<br />\n<br />\n所以我求吓大家<br />\n喺<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>網上、公眾地方</strong></span>要絕對封口<br />\n好大壓力嘅，搵<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>信得過嘅家人、朋友</strong></span><br />\n喺<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>安全、冇外人、冇cam、冇錄音</strong></span>嘅地方抒發晒你嘅感情同壓力<br />\n<br />\n記住有好多鬼會用唔同嘅方法套你資料<br />\n喺呢一刻，只可以相信你<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">現實認識</span></strong>嘅家人、朋友<br />\n<br />\n同時做好我上一個 post 講嘅善後工作<br />\n咁先可以保護到你自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1277426/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1277426/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，如果有人發現自己朋友 / 其他 user 繼續講夢境<br />\n請做以下嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>(1) 連登見到</strong></span></span><br />\n立即留言制止樓主繼續講，再同佢解釋後果，之後求連仔幫手del post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>(2) FB / IG 等社交媒體見到</strong></span></span><br />\n立即 PM 事主，叫佢 del post<br />\n如果有圖同片，你 download 落嚟幫佢 backup<br />\n然後叫佢立即將所有電話、電腦、 手指嘅所有備份刪除<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>(3) TG / Whatsapp 等通訊軟件見到</strong></span></span><br />\n記住 Secret Chat 唔代表完全安全<br />\n而公海 group 更有大量鬼<br />\ndel 到嘅幫佢 del ，del 唔到嘅出聲提醒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>(4) 公眾地方 (學校 / 街 / 餐廳 / 巴士 / 地鐵 etc)</strong></span></span><br />\n喺所有有外人嘅地方，立即制止佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">每人做多少少<br />\n保護呢班戰友<br />\n咁先係真正嘅齊上齊落</span>"},{"pid":"08f9e6ba45fc89f206b6652dd2a417058aa191d3","tid":1281821,"uid":179379,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:33:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n每人做多少少就夠"},{"pid":"78d9343700d24683400912a438e2c59c9e56a6a2","tid":1281821,"uid":179379,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:35:54.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我見好多人仲自爆𡁵<br />\n唔好輸俾白色恐怖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5482b3970cdffade8f196faf1f10f387125c7e0","tid":1281821,"uid":199223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0dcae94949110c74c01171ca062cb294bf44e23","tid":1281821,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:38:55.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"0092352951e8c38105b7535d54e589a4b490b144","tid":1281821,"uid":69672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:40:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"944037128c5b7736290af9cc05ef25f9b8a4ff24","tid":1281821,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:40:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74e746e86f36144a9a440e307a9366190a353151","tid":1281821,"uid":264083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"琴日出街聽到有人好大聲咁討論夢境"},{"pid":"0698fe751dd8e0e82883e22dc73bb6b1df63644b","tid":1281821,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e746e86f36144a9a440e307a9366190a353151","tid":1281821,"uid":264083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"琴日出街聽到有人好大聲咁討論夢境"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:42:41.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"b11f06426a4a338c34c38b4ae7033a167399c5f3","tid":1281821,"uid":179379,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"74e746e86f36144a9a440e307a9366190a353151","tid":1281821,"uid":264083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"琴日出街聽到有人好大聲咁討論夢境"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:43:46.000Z","msg":