"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"0165353fb0fa396373c5945c9eb5c8387f1778de","tid":1281821,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdf5e2df0ce8e806e269de13d75f7d1ee4b4097f","tid":1281821,"uid":47617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"點解要自己禁自己聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"唔理你認唔認同<br />\n現實就係你上網講多咗嘢就會仆街<br />\n<br />\n認真頭盔唔怕戴多幾個<br />\n睇live又好，聽朋友講又好<br />\n點解要話自己做過乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n其實道理同出去要戴口罩一樣<br />\n唔係叫你唔出去<br />\n而係出去都要好好保護自己"},{"pid":"b738dc0c4f72f357303af00b59fa85efe0075395","tid":1281821,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99592c2ab8a923630aa7dd4a8de83cb97ff4551b","tid":1281821,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"我知大家因為白色恐怖好大壓力，我自己都係<br />\n但如你繼續將自己嘅夢境放上網，只會令你更危險<br />\n<br />\n所以我求吓大家<br />\n喺<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>網上、公眾地方</strong></span>要絕對封口<br />\n好大壓力嘅，搵<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>信得過嘅家人、朋友</strong></span><br />\n喺<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>安全、冇外人、冇cam、冇錄音</strong></span>嘅地方抒發晒你嘅感情同壓力<br />\n<br />\n記住有好多鬼會用唔同嘅方法套你資料<br />\n喺呢一刻，只可以相信你<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">現實認識</span></strong>嘅家人、朋友<br />\n<br />\n同時做好我上一個 post 講嘅善後工作<br />\n咁先可以保護到你自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1277426/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1277426/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，如果有人發現自己朋友 / 其他 user 繼續講夢境<br />\n請做以下嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>(1) 連登見到</strong></span></span><br />\n立即留言制止樓主繼續講，再同佢解釋後果，之後求連仔幫手del post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>(2) FB / IG 等社交媒體見到</strong></span></span><br />\n立即 PM 事主，叫佢 del post<br />\n如果有圖同片，你 download 落嚟幫佢 backup<br />\n然後叫佢立即將所有電話、電腦、 手指嘅所有備份刪除<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>(3) TG / Whatsapp 等通訊軟件見到</strong></span></span><br />\n記住 Secret Chat 唔代表完全安全<br />\n而公海 group 更有大量鬼<br />\ndel 到嘅幫佢 del ，del 唔到嘅出聲提醒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>(4) 公眾地方 (學校 / 街 / 餐廳 / 巴士 / 地鐵 etc)</strong></span></span><br />\n喺所有有外人嘅地方，立即制止佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">每人做多少少<br />\n保護呢班戰友<br />\n咁先係真正嘅齊上齊落</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"429b372604471925957b04c4636c40e9216a2604","tid":1281821,"uid":3035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講<br />\n我有權唔解鎖<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我要飲水<br />\n我要食野<br />\n我要去廁所"},{"pid":"e8fb6bea70e1b8a14dc658429a0c1ff6f18a0527","tid":1281821,"uid":54256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:22:54.000Z","msg":"我要驗傷！<br />\n驗傷呀！"},{"pid":"c9bc65250edfb9f2659f68f5488be09697e8db25","tid":1281821,"uid":40672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:24:12.000Z","msg":"我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你 我要驗傷"},{"pid":"547e3791f3fc2fb95857d656df6f52a7945a34d1","tid":1281821,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfd1e0ba246eb8ca49a9e124cc99e4d35501d98d","tid":1281821,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"我發夢。。。。。。我無野講，要見律師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"我睇Live"},{"pid":"1532befdfa4afc28b72b121598b006ee29981357","tid":1281821,"uid":43171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:25:01.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"bdcaf02ad5615516982d722831e9b9d429c72228","tid":1281821,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n真係用下腦"},{"pid":"83b99cedb4ffd5c998c3b5be983f4f29e8414f45","tid":1281821,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"0afcf7e24bf215cb080e